## Patterns Noticed
- All game state is computed on every `/api/state` read (no caching layer); engines are pure functions in `lib/engine/`
- Design tokens are frozen: teal text = `#007E73` (never `#00B8A9`); player bg `#EAF6F5`; Inter font; tap targets ≥44px
- Hungarian copy is verbatim from the `.dc.html` design prototypes in `design_handoff_vbtippjatek_redesign/`
- All dates use `Europe/Budapest` timezone (UTC+2 during tournament)
- Dev server runs on port 3001: `cd /Users/tamasvarga/Documents/GitHub/tomifoci.xyz && pnpm dev`
- Run tests: `cd /Users/tamasvarga/Documents/GitHub/tomifoci.xyz && pnpm test`
